es.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>Located on the local road running from Puerto de Pollensa to Alcudia. The hotel enjoys a sea-front position, which benefits their guests with an unreal views of the bay. To get there from the Palma´s airport, will take you about 45 minutes by car. Palma motorway is the best option, take Via Cintura Oeste, and keep going towards Inca town. Follow the signposts to Puerto de Alcudia town and then to Pollensa. Once you are in Pollensa town, you will see a Puerto de Pollensa signpost (just 6 km away).</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Single - Room offers air conditioning , cable/satellite TV, color TV, Ensuite/ private bathroom, safe in room and telephone.

